\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Wick contraction classes for 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{E}[(\epsilon^{\top}Q\epsilon)^{2}\,\epsilon_{e}\epsilon_{f}]$
\end_inset

,
 with external loose ends 
\begin_inset Formula $e,f$
\end_inset

 shown as crosses.
\end_layout

